description: Simple multi-response app to assist you in deciding if you should go do something. Such as going to get food, going to work or getting food.
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask should i go get coffee?
Alexa ask should I go to work today?
Alexa ask should I go get dressed?
name: Stay or Go?
shortDescription: Simple multi-response app to assist you in deciding if you should go do something.
